	* tagged as mkfbsdmnfst-1.0.6

	* mkfbsdmnfst.cc: Finally get around to fixing dependency
	generation.  Newer versions of FreeBSD require me to open the
	sqlite3 package database using a URI so I can add 'immutable=1' as
	a parameter.  Opening the database in read-only mode (using
	SQLITE_OPEN_READONLY) is not sufficient as a non-root user.

